node.text:
How has back to school & nursery gone this week? Tell us your trials & tribulations of sending your little ones off on a new adventure 👇👇 

And if you’re looking for some inspo for a fun homework space for them, then look no further!! This Ferm Living desk is just one of our many table & chair options for your teeny learners. Swipe to see more 👉👉

📷 from the wonderful @chloeuberkid

node.text:
R E S T O C K

Hello playroom goals 😍🙌 What’s your play space like? Do you have a dedicated room or a corner just for toys? Either way, our gus + beau play mats are the perfect base for fun… building, messy play, racing, jumping & snack time too! Now which pattern to choose 🤔

TAP to shop triangles, now back in stock

📷 thanks to the fantastic @_inpixels

node.text:
N E W  I N 🌈

We’re so excited to share these Mama Designs swaddles, duvet sets & Babasacs with you. Head to stories to hear more about the multi tog design of this clever sleeping bag 💤 It’s perfect for those months when the weather can’t make its mind up & you switch between bed socks & having the fan on, on the daily 🙌 Peace of mind whether it’s chilly OR toasty

TAP to shop

node.text:
M A I L E G

Fun fact: did you know this magical Danish toy brand is pronounced “my lie”? 

Have you started your collection yet?? From mice to bunnies, monkeys, hedgehogs & pandas too, you’re sure to find a new friend. Or two. Or… you get the picture ♥️ 

TAP to shop our favourites

M E M O R I E S

What did your little ones weigh when they were born? We had a 6 lber, a 7 lber & an 8 lber. 

With this fabulous memory box you can record all those precious details to share with your little one, as they grow! It’s also a fab place to store keepsakes like those teeny first shoes ♥️

📷 huge thanks to Hector & his mum @fiandherhouse
